title: Renaissance Art (Art and Artists).pdf
description:
Renaissance Art
Thomson Learning | 1994 | ISBN: 156847217X | English | 56 pages | PDF | 10 MB

A general overview of this rich period in art history, with illustrations of paintings, sculpture, & architecture. One of the first titles to appear in the ART AND ARTISTS series, a history of art in six books. Each title deals with a particular section, period or movement in art, discussing different works of art in relation to their history and the artists themselves. Illustrated in colour and black and white
